Description: Amstrad CPC home computer emulator
 Caprice32 is a software emulator for the Amstrad CPC 8-bit home
 computer series. It faithfully mimics the CPC464, CPC664, and
 CPC6128 models at a low level, ensuring high compatibility with
 original games and software.
 .
 This modern fork brings several enhancements, including:
  * Full emulation of CPC464, CPC664, and CPC6128 models.
  * Preliminary support for the Plus range (464+, 128+, GX4000).
  * Joystick support (physical or mapped to keyboard).
  * Support for disk, tape, and cartridge formats (DSK, IPF,
    CT-RAW, VOC, CDT, CPR) and ZIP archives.
  * Built-in developer tools (debugger, disassembler, memory
    editor).
